## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="6285a-105">次の表に、この属性で許容されるパラメーターと、制御を可能にするプロバイダー構成の側面を示します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6285a-105">The following table lists the parameters accepted by this attribute along with what aspect of the provider configuration it enables you to control.</span></span>  
  
|<span data-ttu-id="6285a-106">パラメーター</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6285a-106">Parameter</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="6285a-107">Winhttp</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6285a-107">Configures</span></span>|  
|---------------|----------------|  
|<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.WmiConfigurationAttribute.Scope>|<span data-ttu-id="6285a-108">プロバイダーがクラスを公開する名前空間。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6285a-108">The namespace in which your provider exposes classes.</span></span>|  
|<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.WmiConfigurationAttribute.NamespaceSecurity>|<span data-ttu-id="6285a-109">-使用される名前空間のセキュリティ (DACL)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6285a-109">-   The security (DACL) on the namespace used.</span></span>|  
|<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.WmiConfigurationAttribute.HostingModel>|<span data-ttu-id="6285a-110">-プロバイダーによって使用されるホスティングモデル。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6285a-110">-   The hosting model that will be used by the provider.</span></span>|  
|<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.WmiConfigurationAttribute.IdentifyLevel>|<span data-ttu-id="6285a-111">-プロバイダーの権限借用モード。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6285a-111">-   The impersonation mode of the provider.</span></span>|  
|<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.WmiConfigurationAttribute.HostingGroup>|<span data-ttu-id="6285a-112">プロバイダーが属するホストグループ。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6285a-112">The hosting group that the provider belongs to.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6285a-113">このパラメーターは、インプロセスプロバイダーにのみ適用されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6285a-113">This parameter only applies to in-process providers.</span></span>|  
|<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.WmiConfigurationAttribute.SecurityRestriction>|<span data-ttu-id="6285a-114">WMI プロバイダーのセキュリティ (DACL)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6285a-114">The security (DACL) on the WMI provider.</span></span>|  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```  
// Specify that this assembly contains code that implements a WMI  
// Provider. Use the assembly:WmiConfiguration attribute to define  
// the WMI namespace, the hosting model, and the impersonation mode  
// of the WMI provider.  
// The attribute below specifies that the class this provider  
// exposes to WMI will be in the root/MortgageCalc namespace, will  
// use the decoupled hosting model and will not allow the provider  
// to impersonate its callers.  
  
[assembly: WmiConfiguration("root/MortgageCalc",HostingModel = ManagementHostingModel.Decoupled, IdentifyLevel = false)]  
```
